name: Marija Meglaj Instagram Model Embbeding
description:
Marija Meglaj @marijameglaj is a Croatian social media starlet who is famous for her eponymous Instagram account (700K followers).

I am releasing two versions, one full at 40k steps, and the earlier one at 31 500 steps. If using both, prompt them by file name. If any of them individually, just prompt "marijameglaj"

I tested across many most popular models as you can see in the example images: Dreamshaper, CuteRichStyle (was fun), ChilloutMix, F222, Dreamlike Diffusion and more.

In the example images, I used one or more add-ons:

  • Deep negative

  • Fashion Girl lora

  • my custom style for fantasy backgrounds in some images
